  ],
  "remarks": "Vladimir Shastin is the Director of Azia Shipping Company LLC. Azia Shipping Company LLC is a Russian shipping company providing logistical support to the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation. In particular, Azia Shipping Company LLC is involved in a military transportation network of Russian cargo vessels shipping North Korean armaments from Pyongyang to military facilities in the Russian port of Dunai. Subsequently, North Korean munitions transported by Azia Shipping Company LLC are transferred to depots on Russia’s western border to be deployed in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}